snippet.title: Particubes - teaser
snippet.description:
Particubes is a virtual space to hang out with friends, play and build anything with colorful cubes.
This is our first teaser! We've been working on this project for months and we expect to welcome our first beta testers in about 2 months. You can register on https://particubes.com. 🙂

If you have questions, please leave a comment here or join our Discord: https://particubes.com/discord

Music by Tai Wuang (https://twitter.com/taiwuang)
